text: Atlético Dos Hermanas Club de Fútbol is a Spanish football team based in Dos Hermanas, in the autonomous community of Andalusia. Founded in 1971 it plays in Regional Preferente de Sevilla, holding home games at Estadio Miguel Román García, with a capacity of 3,200 seats. ==History== Originally known as Dos Hermanas CF, the club
